    <h2>4. Technical Best Practices & Selling Points</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Multi-Tenancy Security:</strong> Hospitals are strictly siloed; Hospital A can never access or see data belonging to Hospital B.</li>
        <li><strong>Automated File Management:</strong> Uploaded bills are automatically renamed and timestamped for clean server storage and easy downloading.</li>
        <li><strong>Admin Protection Logic:</strong> Higher-tier management roles have dashboard access but are restricted from deleting primary Admin accounts.</li>
        <li><strong>Professional Grade UI:</strong> Uses modern typography and a high-end color palette to instill trust and professionalism.</li>
        <li><strong>Hierarchical Workstations:</strong> Each user role lands on a specific dashboard tailored exactly to their job function.</li>
    </ul>

